law.text: The commissioner shall apply the fees set forth in KRS 304.4-010 to risk retention groups. Subtitle 4 of this chapter applies to this subtitle.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 1579, effective July 15, 2010. -- Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 308, sec. 15, effective July 15, 1986.
